msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດຣີເຊັດການລາພັກໄດ້. ໃຫ້ຍົກເລີກ/ລຶບລາຍການນີ້ແລ້ວສ້າງໃໝ່"

#. module: hr_holidays
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_holidays/models/hr_leave_allocation.py:0
msgid ""
"You can't reset an allocation. Cancel/delete this one and create an other"
